track_notes: You can make it shorter, just go to the totem at the trig point and go down the same way; you must park at the village of Saint Leger; plenty room for antennas, nice panorama

You can park near the river, one or two cars; this walk is 1000m up, and 13km, there is some at the middle of the way, in case you miss some! The place on summit is very nice and lot of room for antenna
